channel.title: Looking for Coders
channel.description:
Alright, I've got a basic WinterLove server up and running, basically started from scratch, alot of NPC's are already into the world. But that's about it!
I'm looking for one or 2 people who want to work with my server (name stays secret for now) But I just need people who are willing to give some time into putting some very serious coding into this are really make something!
Of course I'll host everything and take care of that, but what's a server without a team:) If interested please PM me!
Just note that I am not an amateur programmer, I'm just a beginner so I don't know much. :P
Now who wants to start something nobody has ever seen before?!
EDIT**
Switching to new source.. no longer WinterLove
